list.comment:
Some little code improvements:
+ no new tiles spawn now if there is no movement within the table when pressing a arrow key. + tiles only combine once per key press that means [4][4][4][4] -> [0][0][8][8] rather than before: [0][0][0][16]. The new version is the same as in the original game
